Commands:



aclocal
autoheader
automake -ac   (automake -ac --add-misssing   #if readme file is not available)
autoconf
autoreconf -if
libtoolize –force

automake -ac
./configure



Then go to src folder and run:



make
sudo make install

sudo ldconfig



To run the codes:



trisurf –force-from-tape #(first time) or (trisurf --reset-iteration-count)

trisurf #(after that)







